NG0282:1: khyod kyi mdun gyi lhe sna la //
NG0282:3: snang srid dbang du sdud par byed //
NG0282:4: dam nyams mdun gyi srog lha phrol /
NG0282:5: khyod ni stong gsum phra ma mkhan //
NG0282:6: rlung lha'i bu la srin bu'i tsha //
NG0282:7: mchu ni lcags kyi gzong bas rno //
NG0282:8: dam nyams mi dang lha yi bar du dbyen chug cig / khyod kyis mi byed gang yang med //
NG0282:9: lha dang lha min g.yul 'gyed kyang *//
NG0282:10: 'byed par khyod kyis nus par byed //
NG0282:11: tshe gsum dran byed pho rog ma //
NG0282:12: khyod kyis mi dran ci yang med //
NG0282:13: bstan pa gnyen la gnod pa yi //
NG0282:14: dam nyams bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'di //
NG0282:15: 'go bar byed pa'i lha dang phrol //
NG0282:16: stongs par byed pa'i gnyen dang phrol //
NG0282:17: hu lu mun mthong 'ug pa mo //
NG0282:18: khyod kyis mi mthong gang yang med //
NG0282:19: bstan pa gnyen la gnod byed pa'i //
NG0282:20: dam nyams bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'di //
NG0282:21: khyod kyis bsgral ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NG0282:22: ces so so'i sgro gnyis las kyi rlung la phyar ro //
NG0282:23: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:24: zhing bcu lha dang dbye ba'i le'u ste so bdun
NG0282:25: pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das gnod sbyin
NG0282:26: sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te
NG0282:27: / dur khrod chen po'i gnas dag tu //
NG0282:28: dkyil 'khor gru gsum byas nas su //
NG0282:29: steng du sol me rab tu btang *//
NG0282:30: thal chen sol bas nang byugs la //
NG0282:31: zhabs ma dmar po'i gdan bting la //
NG0282:32: ling+ga bya ba'i rgyud nyid la //
NG0282:33: ling+ga rab tu bzos byas la //
NG0282:34: ske nas sngo dmar rab tu gdags //
NG0282:35: drag po rtsang la bstod par bya //
NG0282:36: nag po skra yis skye gnas btags //
NG0282:37: phur pa nyid la bstod par bya //
NG0282:38: rtsa gnyis kyi ni khrag gis byugs //
NG0282:39: thod pa mtshan dang ldan pa ru //
NG0282:40: dmar po gnyis kyi snying khrag la //
NG0282:41: de bzhin bsre ba'i rdzas rnams dang *//
NG0282:42: de bzhin zur la rab tu gzhag / bse phor mtshan ldan nang dag tu //
NG0282:43: chang dang rin chen sna lnga dang *//
NG0282:44: 'bru la sogs te zur du gzhag / tsa ra khrag gis byugs pa yi //
NG0282:45: phur pa'i rtse mo gnam du bstan //
NG0282:46: rab tu zur la dgod par bya //
NG0282:47: de la sogs pa'i rdzas rnams ni //
NG0282:48: snying sna khrag sna mang du \u0f84bsags //
NG0282:49: lha nyid gsal la gnas rnams bsrung *//
NG0282:50: de nyid las su rung ba dang *//
NG0282:51: dregs pa can gyi sngags la 'jug / gong du bstan pa de bzhin du //
NG0282:52: nur ba med pa rab tu bzlas //
NG0282:53: ci bgyi bka' nyan bran ltar khol //
NG0282:54: the tshom som nyi ma yin par //
NG0282:55: dregs pa'i srog snying mang du bzlas //
NG0282:56: hum bstan pa gnyen po bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NG0282:57: rdo rje phur pa'i srung ma dam tshig can //
NG0282:58: khas blangs dam bcas srog gi snying po phul //
NG0282:59: bstan pa rgyas pa'i slad du don mdzad pa'i //
NG0282:60: mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0282:61: dregs pa'i mnga' mdzad gnod sbyin me ru tse /
NG0282:62: khrag mdog dmar po bse yi ral pa can //
NG0282:65: smin ma glog 'gyu bar snang go skabs 'byed //
NG0282:66: shangs nas bu yug rdo rje thog chen 'bebs //
NG0282:67: zhal bgrad tshems ni spu gri 'bum gyis gtams //
NG0282:68: rngam pa'i ljags 'dril bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
NG0282:69: ag tshom dmar ser dug gsum rtsad nas bsreg / snyan nas 'brug stong sgra skad ldi ri ri //
NG0282:70: sen mo lcags kyu'i rtse ltar 'dzin zhing 'gugs //
NG0282:71: ba spu'i nang nas gnam lcags zhun chu 'brub //
NG0282:72: spyan mig dmar pos snang srid gsal bar mdzad //
NG0282:73: lcags kyus snang srid dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NG0282:74: smin ma 'dzings pas me stag rab tu 'phro //
NG0282:75: yak+sha gnod sbyin 'jigs pas rab tu rngam //
NG0282:76: chu ltar 'brub cing me ltar sreg par byed //
NG0282:77: zhabs kyis gang du bsams par yud kyis phyin //
NG0282:78: na bza' dmar po sprin gyi g.yang gzhi gsol //
NG0282:79: nyams pa'i snying 'byin chad par bcug nas gsol //
NG0282:80: rdo rje phur pa'i las rnams khyed kyis sgrubs //
NG0282:81: bcol pa'i las rnams ma lus 'grub par mdzod //
NG0282:82: hum gnod sbyin me ru tse yi thugs dam dgyes skul ma //
NG0282:83: yum gcig rdo rje gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NG0282:84: khros pa'i sku mdog khrag gi thigs pa 'dra //
NG0282:85: mi bzad rdo rje lcags kyi phur pas gtams //
NG0282:86: rdo rje'i ral pa si li li /
NG0282:87: khrag gi mchi ma phru lu lu //
NG0282:88: snying rje mi mnga' dam nyams sgrol bar byed //
NG0282:89: phyag na rdo rje phur pa 'dril zhing 'debs //
NG0282:90: dus la bab bo gar kyi dbang phyug ma //
NG0282:91: gru bzhi srin mo sbrul 'dra ma //
NG0282:92: yab yum rtags dang gdug pa can //
NG0282:93: bya ba ma yin rab tu gzem //
NG0282:94: rta dang byis pa mug pa'am //
NG0282:95: tsag tsog mang po byung ba dang *//
NG0282:96: khug pas rab tu gdab bya ste //
NG0282:97: phur pa blangs shing rab tu 'dril //
NG0282:98: drod dang tshangs pa'i mgo la gdab //
NG0282:99: sa ti yam shud rkang pa la //
NG0282:100: shu la khu le lag pa la //
NG0282:101: da sha gri ba gsang ba la //
NG0282:102: rtsa gnyis yab yum sngags kyis gdab //
NG0282:103: yab snying yum lte rnam pa gnyis //
NG0282:104: rab tu gdab pa de bzhin bya //
NG0282:105: gyad kyi sku mdog bzhir bsgom la //
NG0282:106: phur pa gdab cing las rnams bya //
NG0282:107: gtor ma lag tu thogs byas la //
NG0282:108: srod la zla ba'i 'od la bskul //
NG0282:109: tho rangs skar chen shar nas bskul //
NG0282:110: dgong mo grib so chags la bskul //
NG0282:111: nang par nyi ma'i rtse la bskul //
NG0282:112: rang bzhin rtags ni byung ba dang *//
NG0282:113: gang yin phyogs su gtor ma 'phangs //
NG0282:115: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:116: gnod sbyin dregs pa can sgrub pa'i le'u ste so
NG0282:117: brgyad pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das yon
NG0282:118: tan bstan pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NG0282:119: te / bstan pa thams cad 'phel ba dang *//
NG0282:120: chos nyid zhi bas 'dul ba dang *//
NG0282:121: ma rig rig par 'gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:122: ston pa rang las byung ba dang *//
NG0282:125: rgyud gnyis yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:126: zhi ba chen por rtogs pa dang *//
NG0282:127: ma rig mun pa bsal ba dang *//
NG0282:128: rig pa'i ye shes gsal ba dang *//
NG0282:129: rtogs pas 'bras bur gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:130: dri med 'od ldan gsal ba dag / rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:131: kun bzang don nyid ston pa dang *//
NG0282:132: de nyid gzhi ru gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:133: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa dang *//
NG0282:134: de yis thams cad chos ston dang *//
NG0282:135: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:136: chos nyid phur pa kun gyi gzhi //
NG0282:137: bstan pa dar dang 'dul ba'i don //
NG0282:138: gang du bstan par 'byung bar byed //
NG0282:139: rang bzhin 'dul ba'i don bstan pa //
NG0282:140: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:141: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid 'di //
NG0282:142: chos nyid rig pa kun gyi gzhi //
NG0282:143: rdo rje yang dag skye ba med //
NG0282:144: spros med don rnams rtogs byed pa //
NG0282:145: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:146: thugs rje nam mkha'i byin rlabs las //
NG0282:147: 'dul ba'i don la cir yang ston //
NG0282:149: thams cad ma lus 'dul ba yang *//
NG0282:150: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:151: kun tu bzang po'i ngang nyid las //
NG0282:152: gdug pa 'dul ba'i khro bo yang *//
NG0282:153: hum hum phat phat sgra sgrogs pa //
NG0282:154: yongs su 'dul ba bstan pa yang *//
NG0282:155: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:156: bde bar gshegs pa'i byin rlabs las //
NG0282:157: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i lha //
NG0282:158: rngam pa'i sgra yis kun bkang nas //
NG0282:159: nyon mongs sreg par byed pa'i me //
NG0282:160: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:161: thabs dang shes rab 'brel pa yang *//
NG0282:163: byang chub sems kyi bde ba yang *//
NG0282:164: bde gshegs dgongs pa'i byin rlabs te //
NG0282:165: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:166: 'dod chags sbyong zhing byang chub thob //
NG0282:167: chags pa rang rgyud sdug bsngal sel //
NG0282:168: zhen pa rang rgyud grol bar byed //
NG0282:169: 'dzin pa med cing zhen pa gcod //
NG0282:170: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:171: mkha' la bya ltar 'phur pa dang *//
NG0282:172: chu la mi 'bying mes mi tshig / thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang *//
NG0282:173: mngon shes rab tu mi slu dang *//
NG0282:174: bden pa don dang ldan pa 'di //
NG0282:175: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:176: log pa'i chos can 'dul ba dang *//
NG0282:177: dngos grub bar chad byed pa dang *//
NG0282:178: bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:179: ngan song sdug bsngal mkha' 'gror bcas //
NG0282:180: thugs rje'i byin rlabs 'byung bar ni //
NG0282:181: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:183: zhi dang khro dang 'dul ba'i don //
NG0282:184: 'dul ba'i dbang du de las byung *//
NG0282:185: drang don nges don rnam pa gnyis //
NG0282:187: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:188: rang rgyud dngos por 'joms pa dang *//
NG0282:189: stong pa'i don la dgod pa dang *//
NG0282:190: bden pa'i @#/  / dbyings las 'dul ba dang *//
NG0282:192: zhing bcu'i don rnams mthong ba dang *//
NG0282:193: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:194: nyi ma'i 'od bzhin gsal ba dang *//
NG0282:195: gsal la 'gyur med brtan pa dang *//
NG0282:196: nyes pa med par rtogs pa dang *//
NG0282:197: bgrod du med par mthar phyin pa //
NG0282:198: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:199: skabs dang rim par gyur pa la //
NG0282:200: sa dang lam la de bzhin te //
NG0282:201: rim par nus pa'i byin rlabs dang *//
NG0282:202: 'bras bu'i rim pa de bzhin te //
NG0282:203: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:204: bsam gtan ting 'dzin rim pa ni //
NG0282:205: ting 'dzin rtsal gyi rim pa yis //
NG0282:206: sa la rnam pa gnyis yod de //
NG0282:208: mya ngan 'das pa'i sa lam yang *//
NG0282:209: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:210: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa yang *//
NG0282:211: gang yin rtogs las de bzhin 'byung *//
NG0282:212: ma nges 'dzin pa de bzhin bral //
NG0282:213: 'dzin pa med pa gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:214: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:216: bstan pa yongs kyi 'byung gnas yin //
NG0282:217: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po yin //
NG0282:218: thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas chen yin //
NG0282:219: mun pa sel ba'i sgron me yin //
NG0282:220: rtogs par byed pa'i shes rab yin //
NG0282:221: sgom par byed pa'i bsam gtan yin //
NG0282:222: shes par byed pa'i spyod pa yin //
NG0282:223: thob par byed pa'i 'bras bu yin //
NG0282:224: nges par 'grub pa'i dngos grub yin //
NG0282:225: zhi bar byed pa'i chos nyid yin //
NG0282:226: 'jom par byed pa'i khro bo yin //
NG0282:227: sgrol bar byed pa'i phur pa yin //
NG0282:228: gtub par byed pa'i mtshon cha yin //
NG0282:229: gsal bar byed pa'i mar me yin //
NG0282:230: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:231: rgyud 'byung ba'i don bstan pa'i le'u ste so dgu pa'o ///
NG0282:232: / de nas bcom ldan 'das drag po nyid sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:233: dur khrod chen po'i gnas dag tu //
NG0282:234: drag po gru gsum rim pa bzhin //
NG0282:235: dur khrod rus pa'i phye ma la //
NG0282:236: khrag gis sbrus te rab tu byug / rim pa bzhin du byas kyang rung *//
NG0282:237: rdzas rnams gong du bstan pa bzhin //
NG0282:238: tshang par bsags shing las rnams bya //
NG0282:239: bar chad bsrung zhing byin brlab bya //
NG0282:240: phur pa sngags kyi byin brlab bya //
NG0282:241: brjod kyis rim pas gzhug par bya //
NG0282:243: gtso bo sngags kyis gzir la gzhag / sngags kyi las bya ting 'dzin bsgom //
NG0282:244: rnam gsum bskyed dang mchod pa 'bul //
NG0282:245: las bzhi brdung ba'i sbyor sgrol bya //
NG0282:246: bstab pa'i sngags kyis de bzhin 'bul //
NG0282:247: snying po dril zhing las rnams bya //
NG0282:248: tshogs mchod gong du bstan pa bzhin //
NG0282:249: de yis rtags rnams byung ba dang *//
NG0282:250: rab tu dril zhing drag por bstan //
NG0282:251: gong du bstan pa de min dgos //
NG0282:252: drag po'i las su bstan pa yin //
NG0282:253: mtshan ma brtan po byung ba dang *//
NG0282:255: nya dkyus su bcas pa dang *//
NG0282:256: rang rang drag po bsgral ba'i sngags //
NG0282:257: mtha' yis brten cing gdab par bya //
NG0282:258: dngos por 'dzin pa sgrol ba yi //
NG0282:259: drag po khro bo'i byin rlabs yin //
NG0282:260: dngos po stong par sgrol ba dang *//
NG0282:261: de yi don las mi 'da' dang *//
NG0282:263: mtshon dang dug dang brdung ba dang *//
NG0282:264: bstab dang gnas pa'i rim pa yang *//
NG0282:265: 'dus pa chen po rang rang yin //
NG0282:266: gnas gsum las nyid gang byed kyang *//
NG0282:267: rang rang sngags kyis de bzhin bya //
NG0282:268: tshe dang bkra shis dngos grub kyang *//
NG0282:269: thams cad 'dus pa'i sngags tshig yin //
NG0282:270: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:271: drag po bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bzhi bcu pa'o //
NG0282:272: // de nas bcom ldan 'das sras mchog sgrub pa'i
NG0282:273: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te //
NG0282:274: dur khrod chen po'i gnas dag tu //
NG0282:275: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba bri //
NG0282:276: dur khrod rus pa'i phye ma gdab //
NG0282:277: sngags kyis bsrung zhing phur pa dgod //
NG0282:278: byin brlabs dgod pa sngags nyid yin //
NG0282:279: de nyid bskyed dang spyan drang dang *//
NG0282:280: mchod dang las bzhi'i brdung ba dang *//
NG0282:281: gdab cing bskul zhing snying po bzlas //
NG0282:282: bstod bzhin gong bzhin tshogs mchod byas //
NG0282:283: rtags rnams rab tu byung ba dang *//
NG0282:284: bsgrub pa drag po sngags la 'jug / bsnyen bsgrub sha mdangs phyed par bya //
NG0282:285: brdung ba'i las ni dus dus bya //
NG0282:286: de yis rtags nyid byung ba dang *//
NG0282:287: pho nya dkyus dang yang dag sbyar //
NG0282:288: sgrol ba'i sngags kyis bsgral bar bya //
NG0282:289: phyi ma'i las nyid gong du bstan //
NG0282:290: drag po sgrol ba'i las nyid yin //
NG0282:291: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:292: sras mchog nyid du sgrub pa'i le'u ste zhe gcig
NG0282:293: pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das las mkhan
NG0282:294: dgu bcu sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NG0282:295: zhugs te // dur khrod me ri spungs pa'i sar //
NG0282:296: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba bri //
NG0282:297: sngon du bya ba'i rim pa'i sa //
NG0282:298: gsum dang bzhi bzhi gcig kyang rung *//
NG0282:299: rim pas de bzhin gang yin sbyar //
NG0282:300: so so'i rdzas rnams so sor bsag / thun yang de bzhin rim par bya //
NG0282:301: ting 'dzin rim pa'i byin rlabs las //
NG0282:302: phur pa dar gyi cod pan can //
NG0282:303: mnga' gsol rim pa bzhin du bya //
NG0282:304: mdun du las mkhan de nyid bskyed //
NG0282:305: spyan drang bstim dang mchod pa bya //
NG0282:306: snying po drag po sngags su sbrel //
NG0282:307: lha gsal gang yin las sngags byed //
NG0282:308: bsnyen bsgrub mi dbye gcig tu dril //
NG0282:309: drag por sbrel cing rak+ta sbreng *//
NG0282:310: dus dus rbad cing rab tu khro //
NG0282:311: rtags rnams dbyung ba'i phur pa'i las //
NG0282:312: thun yang de bzhin 'phang bar bya //
NG0282:313: thun la me ru 'bar ba dang *//
NG0282:314: 'od dang skad dang du ba dang *//
NG0282:315: rtags de mngon du 'ong bar bshad //
NG0282:316: bsnyen sngags gdab sngags thun sngags dang *//
NG0282:317: mi dbye de nyid gcig pa yin //
NG0282:320: ting 'dzin rim pa so so yin //
NG0282:321: rdzas kyang mi mthun so so yin //
NG0282:322: bye brag tu ni shes par bya //
NG0282:323: gtso bo gcig la las mkhan ni //
NG0282:324: rkyang pa bcu dgu'i rim pa ste //
NG0282:325: de rnams gang byed las mkhan yin //
NG0282:326: bcu dgu pho mo gnyis su 'dus //
NG0282:327: gang byed ye shes lha la gdags //
NG0282:328: dril bas sngags su gong bzhin 'gro //
NG0282:329: na ya bye brag rigs dang sbyar //
NG0282:330: las kyi pho mo rnam gnyis so //
NG0282:331: gang yin rtags dang sbyar bar bya //
NG0282:332: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:333: las mkhan bcu dgu'i sgrub pa bstan pa'i le'u ste zhe gnyis pa'o ///
NG0282:334: / de nas bcom ldan 'das yon tan gyi ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:335: byin rlabs nam mkha'i ngo bo las //
NG0282:336: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs 'du //
NG0282:337: 'dul ba'i don du cir yang ston //
NG0282:338: thabs mkhas rgyal ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NG0282:340: yang dag don la khyad par med //
NG0282:341: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa 'di //
NG0282:342: 'dul ba'i don du cir yang ston //
NG0282:343: snying po dam pa lha yi sku /
NG0282:344: khams gsum sems can de bzhin 'byung *//
NG0282:345: rtogs dang ma rtogs khyad par med //
NG0282:347: gcig las gnyis su de bzhin snang *//
NG0282:348: snying po'i don la bzang ngan med //
NG0282:349: med pa ma yin cir yang snang *//
NG0282:350: rgyal ba thams cad 'byung bar byed /
NG0282:351: khams gsum sems can 'byung bar byed //
NG0282:352: 'bras bu bzang ngan gnyis su smin //
NG0282:353: rgyal ba'i byin rlabs rnam par 'byung *//
NG0282:354: rgyal ba grangs mang bsam 'das kyang *//
NG0282:355: don dam snying po nyid las byung *//
NG0282:356: rgyud rnams thams cad 'byung ba yang *//
NG0282:357: don dam snying po dbyings las byung *//
NG0282:358: ston pa thams cad 'byung ba yang *//
NG0282:359: don dam snying po dbyings las byung *//
NG0282:360: 'khor rnams thams cad byung ba yang *//
NG0282:361: don dam snying po dbyings las byung *//
NG0282:362: sdud pa thams cad 'byung ba yang *//
NG0282:363: don dam snying po dbyings las byung *//
NG0282:364: theg pa thams cad 'byung ba yang *//
